OL,4,G0100FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GRussell McDonough is in the midst
OL,6,     Gof an outback nightmare, when a
OL,7,     Gtrack collapses under the weight
OL,8,     Gof his rig. Meanwhile, Yogi has
OL,9,     Gsome family time, but trouble
OL,10,     Glies ahead.
OL,11,G0200FTrucking Hell
