OL,13,     Gtasked with rescuing a 26-tonne
OL,14,     Gsewage tanker, loaded with waste
OL,15,     Gmaterial, that has got its wheels
OL,16,     Gwedged in a drainage ditch down a
OL,17,     Gnarrow muddy track.
